Async Loop Cadence
- Each cycle:
  - pick one high-risk module slice
  - prove exploitability/invariant gap
  - apply minimal safe patch
  - run focused verification
  - commit + `codex review --commit`
  - append findings/next slice here
- When marking a slice `completed`:
  - convert next `ready` slice to `in_progress`
  - append at least one new `ready` slice at end of queue
  - append one dependent cross-module slice so the queue stays context-linked (not generic)
